channel.description:

This is text for 32, please paste 86Bit to me on Commenet ;)
Text: @echo off title Running Server "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_24\bin\java.exe" -Xmx1024m -classpath bin;deps/jython.jar;deps/log4j-1.2.15.jar;deps/mina-core-1.1.7.jar;deps/slf4j-api-1.5.3.jar;deps/slf4j-log4j12-1.5.3.jar;deps/xpp3-1.1.4c.jar;deps/xstream-1.3.1-20081003.103259-2.jar com.rs2hd.Main pause
